      <title>欧洲，亚洲面临1300亿美元的列出出埃及记，随着我们的魅力增长</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-19/europe-asia-face-130-billion-listing-exodus-as-us-allure-grows</link>
      <description><![CDATA[欧洲和亚洲公司可能很快就会以新的清单淹没美国市场，因为估值和更深的流动性诱人的诱惑会从其本国市场出发。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-19/europe-asia-face-130-billion-listing-exodus-as-us-allure-grows</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 19 Feb 2025 14:44:23 GMT</pubDate>
